Version:        1.9.4+git20250604.7e38143
Release:        0
Summary:        Console File Manager
License:        GPL-3.0-or-later
Group:          Productivity/File utilities
URL:            https://github.com/ranger/ranger
Source:         %{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
